# Question

Why is it important to study the scriptures every day?

* Learn about Jesus

How is are the scriptures like a compass?

* Help you know what things are bad
* Help you know what things are good
* Can see what other people did and what happened to them
* Drops in bucket

What did you learn?

* Alma taught the gospel
* Anti-Nephi-Lehies didn't fight


